    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m looking to find a new home for my trusty car. It\u2019s been a fantastic ride and is still in really solid shape, perfect for daily commuting or weekend trips! I\u2019ve taken great care of it, so it runs smoothly and looks great too. If you're looking for something reliable and well-loved without the brand-new price tag, this is the one for you. Drop me a message if you want to take it for a spin!",
      "price": 32500.0,
