    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Available is a driver-focused E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54B32 power plant. This unit remains mechanically robust, with the double-VANOS system recently serviced to ensure precise cam phasing. The 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox provides tactile engagement, sending power through a factory-spec 3.62 limited-slip differential. Crucially, the rear subframe has been reinforced with plates to prevent floor fatigue, and the rod bearings have been replaced as preventative maintenance. The chassis remains composed on Bilstein B6 dampers and refreshed control arm bushings. While the exterior shows minor road-going patina, the drivetrain and suspension geometry are dialed in for peak lateral performance. A legitimate enthusiast-grade example with all critical technical vulnerabilities addressed.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 19
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_3",
