    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "This meticulously maintained vehicle offers a perfect balance of reliability and aesthetic appeal. The exterior retains a deep, glossy finish with only minor, age-appropriate signs of road use, while the smoke-free interior features supple upholstery and fully operational electronics. Mechanically, the car is in solid health, backed by a consistent service history, recent fluid changes, and tires with significant tread remaining. It handles with precision and provides a smooth, quiet ride, reflecting the care and attention it has received over the years. This is an ideal choice for a discerning buyer seeking a high-quality, dependable driver that presents beautifully on the road.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
