    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to own. It's in really solid shape and has been super reliable for all my daily trips. If you're looking for a dependable car that still looks great and drives smoothly, you\u2019ve found it! It\u2019s been well-loved and is totally ready for its next adventure. Come by and take it for a spin\u2014I think you're going to love it!",
      "price": 33500.0,
