      "timestep_posted": 19
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Available is a 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine and a Getrag 420G 6-speed manual gearbox. This driver-focused example has undergone professional rear subframe reinforcement and a comprehensive VANOS system overhaul, ensuring the valvetrain remains precise at its 8,000 RPM redline. The chassis dynamics are preserved via a factory-spec limited-slip differential and refreshed bushings across the multi-link rear suspension. While the exterior displays honest patina, the mechanical vitals\u2014including compression across all six cylinders and throttle body synchronization\u2014are within optimal tolerances. This is a mechanically sorted performance machine ready for spirited corner carving.",
